name: python-leveldb
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.193" %}

package:
  name: python-leveldb
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: leveldb-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://pypi.python.org/packages/source/l/leveldb/leveldb-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  md5: 2952434f2a0ce10c44f58542cc561589

build:
  skip: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
  build:
    - leveldb
    - python
    - setuptools

  run:
    - leveldb
    - python

test:
  imports:
    - leveldb

about:
  home: http://code.google.com/p/py-leveldb/
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  summary: Python bindings for leveldb database library

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
